---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy and Cookies Policy - Mónica Montúfar" description="Privacy and cookies policy of Mónica Montúfar." lang="en">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 min-h-screen">
    <a href="/en" class="text-primary hover:text-white mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 group transition-colors">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_back</span>
      Back to Home
    </a>
    
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-12 text-white">Privacy and Cookies Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none font-light leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-8"><em>Last updated: April 1st, 2026</em></p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">1. Personal Data Processing</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        In accordance with current data protection regulations, we inform you that the information collected in the forms on this website will be used exclusively for the sole purpose of notifying you about the project's launch and maintaining a direct communication channel. We promise not to send unsolicited commercial communications (spam) and to safeguard your information with high technical and organizational security standards.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">2. What are Cookies?</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        A cookie is a small text file that a website stores on your computer or mobile device when you visit it. We use cookies to understand how you interact with our site, improve your browsing experience, and ensure the correct technical functioning of the website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Essential Cookies (Technical):</strong> These are strictly necessary for the site to function and cannot be disabled. For example, your persistent preference regarding this very privacy notice.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytical Cookies:</strong> These allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our website through tools like anonymized Google Analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">4. User Rights</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        You have the right to access, rectify, or delete your personal data at any time. You can also revoke your previously granted consent. For any inquiry regarding privacy or cookie management, please contact us through the institutional channels provided when this page officially opens.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
